model.item
Class Item

java.lang.Object
  model.common.Model
      model.item.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<IModel>, IModel
public class Item
extends Model

The Item class encapsulates all the funtions and data associated with a "Item". It extends the ItemData class which contains getters and setters for the various datas.
